  "texts": [
    "Another limitation of our work is the methodology of document embedding.",
    "We chose a bag-of-words approach, where we obtained embeddings for single words and aggregated them by document.",
    "The most serious problem with this methodology is that the embedding vector for each word is consistent over time.",
    "In this regard, we need to consider the context of the word used in each document.",
    "There has been tremendous progress in the methodology of contextual word embedding, such as bidirectional encoder representation with transformation (BERT)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}